name: Pressure Tank Compressor
details:
Caline's Pressure Tank is a natural sounding compressor, that will do it all from chickin' pickin' squish to power chord and solo boosting and leveling. Compressors are the hidden gems of effects, a useful tool to clarify single note attack and even out chord stomps.
Level, EQ, Comp Controls
True Bypass
Super Solid Metal Casing
Uses 9V Battery or Standard Boss Style Adapter (not included)
